nabled":true,"tab_3_title":"Belt Care & Storage","tab_3_content_type":"richtext","tab_3_metafield":"","tab_3_richtext":"<h3>How should I care for my Four Four leather belt?<\/h3><p>Luxury deserves care. To preserve the beauty and longevity of your Four Four belt:<\/p><p>Avoid excessive moisture – Keep it dry to maintain the integrity of the leather.<\/p><p>Use a leather conditioner – Periodically nourish the leather to keep it supple and prevent cracking.<\/p><p>Clean with a soft cloth – Gently wipe away dust and dirt to maintain its pristine finish.<\/p><h3>How should I store my Four Four belt?<\/h3><p>A well-preserved belt is one that ages beautifully. Ensure proper storage by:<\/p><p>Hanging on a belt rack to maintain its natural shape.<\/p><p>Rolling instead of folding to prevent creases and cracks.<\/p><p>Keeping it in the Four Four dust bag – Every belt arrives with a custom-designed dust bag, offering protection from dust, humidity, and scratches.<\/p><h3>Can I travel with my Four Four belt?<\/h3><p>Yes. To keep your belt in its best condition while travelling:<\/p><p>Roll it inside its dust bag for compact storage.<\/p><p>Avoid overpacking to prevent unnecessary pressure.<\/p><p>Whether at home or on the move, your Four Four belt remains a refined essential, always ready to complement your wardrobe.<\/p>","tab_4_enabled":false,"tab_4_title":"Additional Info","tab_4_content_type":"metafield","tab_4_metafield":"","tab_4_richtext":"","tab_alignment":"center","mobile_tab_alignment":"center","content_alignment":"center","animation_type":"slide","animation_duration":1,"tab_font_size":16,"tab_text_transform":"uppercase","tab_padding_vertical":12,"tab_padding_horizontal":16,"tab_spacing":8,"tab_text_color":"#666666","tab_hover_color":"#ffd700","tab_active_color":"#000000","active_indicator_height":2,"active_indicator_color":"#000000","border_width":1,"border_color":"#e6e6e6","content_spacing":24,"content_font_size":14,"content_text_color":"#000000","content_heading_